<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4542143>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 18. Dichotomius validipilosus (Luederwaldt, 1931). A–B. Dorsal habitus. A. ♂. B. ♀. C. Lateral view of the aedeagus.D. View from above of the head, basal third surface subrugose. E. Ventral view of the aedeagus. F–G. Lamella copulatrix. H. Punctures along the anterior margin of the punctuated, sixth sternite marginally lower, depressed." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4542143/files/figure.png" .

